// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2714 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 15225ba1-5539-5a0c-b3de-f552f25df144

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:1*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*")
